Thrifting therapy🧘🏼‍♂️ // @savers_thrift

Adventuring with @brianaclegg, sprucing up our home decor and grabbing some clothing for the Summer!

We never know what cool things may spark our imagination while thrifting. I grabbed a few pieces for the office, but my favorite was the CFC t-shirt. It has a nice boxy fit with a simple print that makes it easy to incorporate. Gotta make sure to check in each section for tucked away gems or garments that may not be your typical size, but fit great!

#thriftproud #SaversPartner #ValueVillagePartner #streetwear #thrifting

Let’s soak up the summer🌊 // @sperry #ad

New to boat shoes, but not new to this! This style of shoe definitely puts an elevated spin on my outfit.

#SperrySummerEdit #SperryStyle #casualwear #fashion #style

Lately I have been inspired to bring more unique cut and sewn pieces to life- leveling up each detail in my productions.

@vicissitude

The next release for my brand welcomes of a few pairs of denim, which is a newer area for me. I’ve really enjoyed dialing in the techniques for sourcing, sewing, and finishing denim, and can’t wait to share!

#entrepeneur #manufacturing #cutandsew #privatelabel #clothingbrand

Love bringing new life to once-loved items♻️ // @savers_thrift

Thrifting is one of my favorite ways to find unique clothing or get inspiration for my outfits. Having such a large variety of styles available at your fingertips helps a ton when looking for that finishing piece, or a staple to start with.

Don’t be afraid to get creative with your thrifted garments; Do they have good bones? Can it be cropped, tapered, or hemmed? ✂️
